name: Going Back Home
description:
Going Back Home (GBH0303-2017)

Home isn't it? The final destination of our journey, I said. The place where you can talk loudly with your ownself, I said. The place where you can cry yourself out, I said. Then I solely ask to myself, am I home yet?

"Going Back Home" series is talking about how we desperately miss our home regardless of what condition of our home is.
